page_title: How to migrate to OpenAI Python v1.x
page_description: Learn about migrating to the latest release of the OpenAI Python library with Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: Authentication```pythonfrom azure.identity import DefaultAzureCredential, get_bearer_token_providerfrom openai import AzureOpenAItoken_provider = get_bearer_token_provider(DefaultAzureCredential(), "https://cognitiveservices.azure.com/.default")api_version = "2024-02-01"endpoint = "https://my-resource.openai.azure.com"client = AzureOpenAI(    api_version=api_version,    azure_endpoint=endpoint,    azure_ad_token_provider=token_provider,)completion = client.chat.completions.create(    model="deployment-name",  # model = "deployment_name"    messages=[        {            "role": "user",            "content": "How do I output all files in a directory using Python?",        },    ],)print(completion.model_dump_json(indent=2))```
